title: Artist Spotlight: Scott Campbell and the Scab Shop Tattoo Art And Culture Pass
description: Renowned Tattoo artist Scott Campbell teams up with co-founder Josh Hubberman and a collection of top-tier artists to transform the Tattoo industry via NFT Shop Passes. Proof Collective members will have allowlist access on mint day with a total limit of 5000 passes available.
